- I'll do the worrying.

01:10:01.487 --> 01:10:02.545
Here, watch that clamp.

01:10:02.622 --> 01:10:04.055
Pick up stitch.

01:10:05.058 --> 01:10:07.618
Come on, come on.

01:10:07.694 --> 01:10:09.753
Load the Milrinone.

01:10:09.829 --> 01:10:12.161
Just give me time. We need to move.

01:10:19.806 --> 01:10:22.331
Come here.

01:10:22.408 --> 01:10:24.933
- What the fuck is going on?
- Relax.

01:10:25.011 --> 01:10:26.239
Look, what did I tell you?

01:10:26.312 --> 01:10:27.836
I told you I was going
to look after you, didn't I?

01:10:27.914 --> 01:10:30.610
You trusted me this far,
so just keep quiet.

01:10:30.683 --> 01:10:33.151
I almost forgot.

01:10:33.219 --> 01:10:36.086
I've had this way too long
to leave this behind.

01:10:37.223 --> 01:10:38.520
Three-one.

01:10:38.591 --> 01:10:41.560
Wet his hands.

01:10:41.628 --> 01:10:43.027
John, we're running out of time.

01:10:43.096 --> 01:10:44.961
We're almost there.
We're almost there.

01:10:45.031 --> 01:10:46.157
Scissor.

01:10:46.232 --> 01:10:47.597
Cut.

01:10:49.135 --> 01:10:52.502
Head down, pressure down.

01:10:52.572 --> 01:10:55.268
Cross clamp off.

01:10:58.745 --> 01:11:01.145
- We got rhythm.
- Looks good.

01:11:06.452 --> 01:11:07.783
I can't go with you.

01:11:11.190 --> 01:11:12.122
What?

01:11:12.191 --> 01:11:14.182
They want you.

01:11:14.260 --> 01:11:17.821
You're the one who
injected the heart, not me.

01:11:17.897 --> 01:11:19.194
They don't want me.

01:11:21.901 --> 01:11:23.198
Sam.

01:11:23.269 --> 01:11:26.500
I'm sorry.

01:11:26.572 --> 01:11:29.473
I'm just the grieving
widow, remember?

01:11:33.179 --> 01:11:34.407
I didn't do anything wrong.

01:11:34.480 --> 01:11:36.107
- Yeah, you did.
- No!

01:11:39.018 --> 01:11:41.384
Going to be kind of hard
to play a grieving widow

01:11:41.454 --> 01:11:43.388
with your fingerprints
all on the syringe.

01:11:43.456 --> 01:11:46.254
Jack.

01:11:46.325 --> 01:11:48.520
Jack, come on.

01:11:48.594 --> 01:11:49.526
Let me in.

01:11:50.663 --> 01:11:52.153
Jack.

01:11:52.231 --> 01:11:54.222
Come on.

01:11:54.300 --> 01:11:56.564
Please?

01:11:56.636 --> 01:11:58.831
Goddamn you.
Open the fucking door.

01:11:58.905 --> 01:12:00.736
Open the door now!

01:12:00.807 --> 01:12:02.934
Jack, please!

01:12:03.009 --> 01:12:03.976
Open the fucking door.

01:12:04.043 --> 01:12:05.567
Bye, Sam.

01:12:05.645 --> 01:12:07.408
Jack!

01:12:14.153 --> 01:12:16.383
Closing the chest. Pressure okay?

01:12:16.456 --> 01:12:18.788
No Vicryl.

01:12:18.858 --> 01:12:20.052
Sop it wet.

01:12:20.126 --> 01:12:21.957
Yeah.

01:12:22.028 --> 01:12:23.188
Scissor, please.

01:12:25.164 --> 01:12:26.631
Cut.

01:12:33.272 --> 01:12:34.330
Great job.

01:12:34.407 --> 01:12:35.738
Well, we do what we can.

01:12:35.808 --> 01:12:37.105
Amazing.

01:12:40.079 --> 01:12:41.011
God damn it.

01:12:41.080 --> 01:12:43.514
- He's in fib.
- Shit.

01:12:43.583 --> 01:12:45.642
Get me an amp of eppy now.

01:12:45.718 --> 01:12:46.946
Clay.

01:12:47.019 --> 01:12:48.509
Come on, Clayton.

01:12:48.588 --> 01:12:50.579
I'm trying to be a hero here.
Don't make me look bad.

01:12:52.091 --> 01:12:53.888
I'm going to stay here with you.

01:12:53.960 --> 01:12:56.155
There's no one left
for me out there anyway.

01:12:56.229 --> 01:12:57.753
You don't need anyone else.

01:12:57.830 --> 01:13:00.264
You do it yourself, Clay.

01:13:00.333 --> 01:13:02.198
- You're strong.
- I'm not him.

01:13:02.268 --> 01:13:03.496
I tried, Mom.

01:13:03.569 --> 01:13:06.902
Really, I did, but...
I'm just not him.

01:13:06.973 --> 01:13:07.962
He's still in fib.

01:13:08.040 --> 01:13:09.803
- Clay.
- Never going to be.

01:13:09.876 --> 01:13:12.242
- Charge the paddles.
- I don't want you to be.

01:13:12.311 --> 01:13:13.972
We're losing him.

01:13:17.049 --> 01:13:18.073
200.

01:13:18.151 --> 01:13:19.209
Clear.

01:13:20.620 --> 01:13:21.552
Come on.

01:13:21.621 --> 01:13:24.249
I have to show you something.

01:13:24.323 --> 01:13:25.813
I don't want to see this.

01:13:25.892 --> 01:13:27.450
I'm afraid you have to.

01:13:27.527 --> 01:13:30.462
<i>Remember, Clay?</i>

01:13:30.530 --> 01:13:33.363
I am remembering.

01:13:33.432 --> 01:13:35.900
I'm watching the TV.
What do you want from me?

01:13:35.968 --> 01:13:37.492
No, you're not. Look.

01:13:39.906 --> 01:13:41.396
You're listening.

01:13:41.474 --> 01:13:42.941
