- Charge.

01:14:05.131 --> 01:14:06.155
Clear.

01:14:09.135 --> 01:14:10.102
Daddy?

01:14:12.872 --> 01:14:15.363
Hey! Hey! Stop talking.

01:14:18.845 --> 01:14:20.107
Dad.

01:14:20.179 --> 01:14:23.148
All right, I heard you the first time!

01:14:23.216 --> 01:14:25.878
Come on, Clayton. It's Christmas.

01:14:25.952 --> 01:14:27.681
Put it on.

01:14:27.753 --> 01:14:29.015
Ah!

01:14:29.088 --> 01:14:31.818
- Daddy, please!
- Fucking bitch. Jesus!

01:14:31.891 --> 01:14:33.518
Don't you two ever shut up?

01:14:33.593 --> 01:14:35.288
This is what you want, Lilith, isn't it?

01:14:35.361 --> 01:14:36.623
Huh? How's this look?

01:14:36.696 --> 01:14:37.685
This make you happy?

01:14:37.763 --> 01:14:38.821
Daddy, please!

01:14:38.898 --> 01:14:39.830
All right. That's it!

01:14:39.899 --> 01:14:41.264
Please leave him alone.

01:14:41.334 --> 01:14:43.325
Couldn't keep your mouth shut,
could you, Clay?

01:14:43.402 --> 01:14:44.562
- Clayton.
- Come here.

01:14:44.637 --> 01:14:46.662
- Please.
- Come here!

01:14:46.739 --> 01:14:47.865
- Clayton!
- Come here!

01:14:59.819 --> 01:15:01.753
