01:15:35.354 --> 01:15:36.787
- Still in fib.
- Give me 360.

01:15:36.856 --> 01:15:39.450
- We lost him.
- No. Again.

01:15:39.525 --> 01:15:41.618
- 360.
- Clear.

01:15:49.235 --> 01:15:51.669
You didn't want to remember, Clay.

01:15:53.839 --> 01:15:55.966
I let you forget
because I thought the truth

01:15:56.042 --> 01:16:00.411
would be too hard to live with.

01:16:00.479 --> 01:16:03.380
I thought I was protecting you.

01:16:03.449 --> 01:16:07.351
But all I did
was cause you more pain.

01:16:07.420 --> 01:16:09.581
I am so sorry.

01:16:12.024 --> 01:16:16.222
I'm not proud
of what I became, Clay,

01:16:16.295 --> 01:16:19.526
but I am proud
of what you've become.

01:16:19.598 --> 01:16:22.658
You're a hundred times
the man he was.

01:16:25.237 --> 01:16:27.205
You always were.

01:16:38.684 --> 01:16:41.209
It's time for you to live.

01:17:07.346 --> 01:17:08.313
Clayton...

01:17:08.381 --> 01:17:09.848
